title: Art Memory Game
description:
Art Memory Game developed from various artworks from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

The art of a good memory takes practice!  Sharpen your skills with our 48 card game featuring works from our permanent collection.  Can you recognize works by: Claude Monet, Georgia O’Keeffe, Alfred Stieglitz and many more?  Match coordinating works of art to win. Game is for 1 or more players.

  • Card Dimensions: 3 x 3 in.
  • Box Dimensions: 6.25 x 6.25 in.
  • Box has magnetic closure.
